code: /**  * Appender is the name of the pax appender that need to be configured in the PaxLogging service configuration.  */ public String getAppender() {     return appender. }
/**  * @deprecated use {@link #getAppender()}  */ @Deprecated public String getName() {     return getAppender(). }
public Producer createProducer() throws Exception {     throw new RuntimeCamelException("Cannot produce to a PaxLoggingEndpoint: " + getEndpointUri()). }
public Consumer createConsumer(Processor processor) throws Exception {     PaxLoggingConsumer answer = new PaxLoggingConsumer(this, processor).     configureConsumer(answer).     return answer. }
